data.description: Charming 3-bed brick ranch home with 1,449 square feet of living space. You will love the large windows letting in tons of natural light and sparkling oak hardwood flooring throughout. The updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances opens to a dining room and living room. Enjoy a large, fully-fenced backyard and the convenience of an oversized one-car garage. Located just minutes from Town Center Virginia Beach, the Chesapeake Bay, and Lake Smith recreation in a wonderful neighborhood. Your dream home awaits, come see it today!
